2. **Analyzing the Given Income Statement**: Looking at the provided income statement, we can see a line item labeled "Financial Expenses" with an amount of "351260.94" dated "2024-02-05".

   - No other line items (like "Interest Income") represent costs; they are either revenues or other types of expenses.
